            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Nylons</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Nylon is a synthetic polymer that is not biodegradable and can persist in the environment for hundreds of years. It is
                commonly used in fishing gear, packaging, and textiles, and when discarded, it can entangle and harm marine life.
              </p>
              <!-- <a href="#!" class="btn btn-primary">Button</a> -->
            </div>
