            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Recylced plastics</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Recycled plastics, while a step towards sustainability, can also be a source of pollution if not properly managed. When
                recycled plastics are contaminated or improperly disposed of, they can release harmful chemicals into the environment
                and contribute to the buildup of plastic waste.
              </p>
              <!-- <a href="#!" class="btn btn-primary">Button</a> -->
